sentence: list wednesday night flights from oakland to salt lake city [beep]
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v0.flight_id||'"', '"'||v1.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v5.days_code||'"', '"'||v5.day_name||'"', v0.departure_time FROM flight v0,
 airport_service v1, city v2,
 airport_service v3, city v4, days v5 
WHERE (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) 
AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code) 
AND (v2.city_name = 'OAKLAND'))) AND (((v0.to_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) 
AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) 
AND (v4.city_name = 'SALT LAKE CITY'))) AND ((((v0.flight_days = ANY v5.days_code) 
AND (v5.day_name = 'WEDNESDAY')) AND ((v0.departure_time >=  1800) 
AND (v0.departure_time <=  2359))) OR (((v0.flight_days = ANY v5.days_code) 
AND (v5.day_name = 'THURSDAY')) 
AND ((v0.departure_time >=  0) AND (v0.departure_time <=  600))))));
sql: ( SELECT DISTINCT FLIGHT.FLIGHT_ID FROM FLIGHT WHERE ( FLIGHT . FROM_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' OAKLAND ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' SALT LAKE CITY ' ) ) AND ( ( FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' WEDNESDAY ' ) AND ( FLIGHT.DEPARTURE_TIME > = 1800 AND FLIGHT.DEPARTURE_TIME < = 2359 ) ) OR ( FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' THURSDAY ' ) AND ( FLIGHT.DEPARTURE_TIME > = 0 AND FLIGHT.DEPARTURE_TIME < = 600 ) ) ) ) ) ) ;
